{"id":771,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":771,"title":"Jeremiah 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The people of Judah forsook the Lord, the fountain of living waters—They worshipped idols and rejected the prophets."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.1","order":"02.25.002.50692"},["b","1"],"Moreover the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came to me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.2","order":"02.25.002.50693"},["b","2"],"Go and cry in the ears of Jerusalem, saying, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; I remember thee, the kindness of thy youth, the love of thine espousals,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"when"],"thou wentest after me in the wilderness, in a land",["i","that was"],"not sown."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.3","order":"02.25.002.50694"},["b","3"],"Israel",["i","was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"holiness"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","and"],"the firstfruits of his increase: all that devour him shall offend; evil shall come upon them, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.4","order":"02.25.002.50695"},["b","4"],"Hear ye the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", O house of Jacob, and all the families of the house of Israel:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.5","order":"02.25.002.50696"},["b","5"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", What iniquity have your fathers found in me, that they are gone far from me, and have walked after vanity, and are become vain?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.6","order":"02.25.002.50697"},["b","6"],"Neither said they, Where",["i","is"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that brought us up out of the land of Egypt, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"led"],"us through the wilderness, through a land of deserts and of pits, through a land of drought, and of the shadow of death, through a land that no man passed through, and where no man dwelt?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.7","order":"02.25.002.50698"},["b","7"],"And I brought you into a plentiful country, to eat the fruit thereof and the goodness thereof; but when ye entered, ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"defiled"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"land"],", and made mine heritage an abomination."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.8","order":"02.25.002.50699"},["b","8"],"The priests said not, Where",["i","is"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"? and they that handle the law knew me not: the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"pastors"],"also transgressed against me, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"prophets"],"prophesied by Baal, and walked after",["i","things that"],"do not profit."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.9","order":"02.25.002.50700"},["b","9"],"¶Wherefore I will yet plead with you, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and with your children’s children will I plead."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.10","order":"02.25.002.50701"},["b","10"],"For pass",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"over"],"the isles of Chittim, and see; and send unto Kedar, and consider diligently, and see if there be such a thing."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.11","order":"02.25.002.50702"},["b","11"],"Hath a nation changed",["i","their"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"gods"],", which",["i","are"],"yet no gods? but my people have changed their glory for",["i","that which"],"doth not profit."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.12","order":"02.25.002.50703"},["b","12"],"Be astonished, O ye heavens, at this, and be horribly afraid, be ye very desolate, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.13","order":"02.25.002.50704"},["b","13"],"For my people have committed two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"evils"],"; they have forsaken me the fountain of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"living waters"],",",["i","and"],"hewed them out cisterns, broken cisterns, that can hold no water."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.14","order":"02.25.002.50705"},["b","14"],"¶",["i","Is"],"Israel a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"servant"],"?",["i","is"],"he a homeborn",["i","slave?"],"why is he spoiled?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.15","order":"02.25.002.50706"},["b","15"],"The young lions roared upon him,",["i","and"],"yelled, and they made his land waste: his cities are burned without inhabitant."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.16","order":"02.25.002.50707"},["b","16"],"Also the children of Noph and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Tahapanes"],"have broken the crown of thy head."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.17","order":"02.25.002.50708"},["b","17"],"Hast thou not procured this unto thyself, in that thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"forsaken"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, when he led thee by the way?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.18","order":"02.25.002.50709"},["b","18"],"And now what hast thou to do in the way of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Egypt"],", to drink the waters of Sihor? or what hast thou to do in the way of Assyria, to drink the waters of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"the river"],"?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.19","order":"02.25.002.50710"},["b","19"],"Thine own wickedness shall correct thee, and thy backslidings shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"reprove"],"thee: know therefore and see that",["i","it is"],"an evil",["i","thing"],"and bitter, that thou hast forsaken the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, and that my fear",["i","is"],"not in thee, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.20","order":"02.25.002.50711"},["b","20"],"¶For of old time I have broken thy yoke,",["i","and"],"burst thy bands; and thou saidst, I will not transgress; when upon every high hill and under every green tree thou wanderest, playing the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"harlot"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.21","order":"02.25.002.50712"},["b","21"],"Yet I had planted thee a noble",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"vine"],", wholly a right seed: how then art thou turned into the degenerate plant of a strange vine unto me?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.22","order":"02.25.002.50713"},["b","22"],"For though thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"wash"],"thee with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"nitre"],", and take thee much soap,",["i","yet"],"thine iniquity is marked before me, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.23","order":"02.25.002.50714"},["b","23"],"How canst thou say, I am not polluted, I have not gone after Baalim? see thy way in the valley, know what thou hast done:",["i","thou art"],"a swift dromedary traversing her ways;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.24","order":"02.25.002.50715"},["b","24"],"A wild ass used to the wilderness,",["i","that"],"snuffeth up the wind at her pleasure; in her occasion who can turn her away? all they that seek her will not weary themselves; in her month they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"shall find her"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.25","order":"02.25.002.50716"},["b","25"],"Withhold thy foot from being unshod, and thy throat from thirst: but thou saidst, There is no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"hope"],": no; for I have loved strangers, and after them will I go."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.26","order":"02.25.002.50717"},["b","26"],"As the thief is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"ashamed"],"when he is found, so is the house of Israel ashamed; they, their kings, their princes, and their priests, and their prophets,"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.27","order":"02.25.002.50718"},["b","27"],"Saying to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"a stock"],", Thou",["i","art"],"my father; and to a stone, Thou hast brought me forth: for they have turned",["i","their"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"back"],"unto me, and not",["i","their"],"face: but in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"time"],"of their trouble they will say, Arise, and save us."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.28","order":"02.25.002.50719"},["b","28"],"But where",["i","are"],"thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"gods"],"that thou hast made thee? let them arise, if they can save thee in the time of thy trouble: for",["i","according to"],"the number of thy cities are thy gods, O Judah."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.29","order":"02.25.002.50720"},["b","29"],"Wherefore will ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"plead"],"with me? ye all have transgressed against me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.30","order":"02.25.002.50721"},["b","30"],"In vain have I smitten your children; they received no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"correction"],": your own sword hath devoured your prophets, like a destroying lion."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.31","order":"02.25.002.50722"},["b","31"],"¶O generation, see ye the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". Have I been a wilderness unto Israel? a land of darkness? wherefore say my people, We are lords; we will come no more unto thee?"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.32","order":"02.25.002.50723"},["b","32"],"Can a maid forget her ornaments,",["i","or"],"a bride her attire? yet my people have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"forgotten"],"me days without number."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.33","order":"02.25.002.50724"},["b","33"],"Why trimmest thou thy way to seek love? therefore hast thou also taught the wicked",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"ones"],"thy ways."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.34","order":"02.25.002.50725"},["b","34"],"Also in thy skirts is found the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"blood"],"of the souls of the poor innocents: I have not found it by secret search, but upon all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"these"],"."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.35","order":"02.25.002.50726"},["b","35"],"Yet thou sayest, Because I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"innocent"],", surely his anger shall turn from me. Behold, I will plead with thee, because thou sayest, I have not sinned."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.36","order":"02.25.002.50727"},["b","36"],"Why gaddest thou about so much to change thy way? thou also shalt be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"ashamed"],"of Egypt, as thou wast ashamed of Assyria."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.37","order":"02.25.002.50728"},["b","37"],"Yea, thou shalt go forth from him, and thine hands upon thine head: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath rejected thy confidences, and thou shalt not prosper in them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.2a","order":"02.25.002.50729"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.26.26-29"},"1 Ne. 17:26 (26–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.3a","order":"02.25.002.50731"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/28.36"},"Ex. 28:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/23.18"},"Isa. 23:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.6a","order":"02.25.002.50733"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/107.4"},"Ps. 107:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.7a","order":"02.25.002.50735"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/16.18"},"Jer. 16:18"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pollution"},"TG Pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.7b","order":"02.25.002.50737"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3"},"Hosea 9:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.8a","order":"02.25.002.50739"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shepherd"},"TG Shepherd"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.8b","order":"02.25.002.50741"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.10a","order":"02.25.002.50743"},["b","10a"],["span.small","OR"],"over to."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.11a","order":"02.25.002.50745"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.13a","order":"02.25.002.50747"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.13b","order":"02.25.002.50749"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/living-water"},"TG Living Water"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.14a","order":"02.25.002.50751"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.22.22-23"},"Ex. 4:22 (22–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.16a","order":"02.25.002.50753"},["b","16a"],["span.small","IE"],"Tahapanhes, in Egypt, in the land of Goshen.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/43.7.7-8"},"Jer. 43:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.1"},"44:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.17a","order":"02.25.002.50755"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.18a","order":"02.25.002.50757"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.2.1-2"},"Isa. 30:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.18b","order":"02.25.002.50759"},["b","18b"],["span.small","IE"],"the Euphrates."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.19a","order":"02.25.002.50761"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproof"},"TG Reproof"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.20a","order":"02.25.002.50763"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.21a","order":"02.25.002.50765"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vineyard-of-the-lord"},"TG Vineyard of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.22a","order":"02.25.002.50767"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wash"},"TG Wash"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.22b","order":"02.25.002.50769"},["b","22b"],["span.small","IE"],"alkali; carbonate of soda."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.24a","order":"02.25.002.50771"},["b","24a"],["span.small","JST"],"Jer. 2:24 … shall",["i","not"],"find her."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.25a","order":"02.25.002.50773"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/18.12"},"Jer. 18:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.26a","order":"02.25.002.50775"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.27a","order":"02.25.002.50777"},["b","27a"],["span.small","OR"],"wood; i.e., an idol.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.9"},"Jer. 3:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.27b","order":"02.25.002.50779"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/18.17"},"Jer. 18:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/32.33"},"32:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.16"},"Ezek. 8:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"27c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.27c","order":"02.25.002.50781"},["b","27c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.24.22-25"},"Mosiah 11:24 (22–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.7.7-9"},"D&C 101:7 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.28a","order":"02.25.002.50783"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/10.14.13-14"},"Judg. 10:14 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/3.13"},"2 Kgs. 3:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/1.28.27-28"},"Prov. 1:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.29a","order":"02.25.002.50785"},["b","29a"],["span.small","HEB"],"quarrel, contend."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.30a","order":"02.25.002.50787"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastening"},"TG Chastening"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.32a","order":"02.25.002.50789"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/18.15"},"Jer. 18:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.33a","order":"02.25.002.50791"},["b","33a"],["span.small","HEB"],"women."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.34a","order":"02.25.002.50793"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.38"},"Ps. 106:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.4"},"Jer. 19:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.34b","order":"02.25.002.50795"},["b","34b"],["span.small","IE"],"their clothing."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.35a","order":"02.25.002.50797"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.14.9-15"},"Mosiah 12:14 (9–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/21.6"},"Alma 21:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.36a","order":"02.25.002.50799"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.5.3,5"},"Isa. 30:5 (3, 5)"],"."]]}
